      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Mike Clarke</b>\n</p><p><b>Michael R.B. (Mike) Clarke</b> († 1994),<br />\nwas a British statistician and computer scientist at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institute_of_Computer_Science\">University of London Institute of Computer Science (ICS)</a>, since 1974, head of CS and Statistics at <a href=\"/Queen_Mary,_University_of_London\" title=\"Queen Mary, University of London\">Queen Mary, University of London</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. He researched and published on computer chess, organized the <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_3\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 3\">Advances in Computer Chess 3</a> conference, 1981 in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London\">London</a>, and was editor of the proceedings of <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_1\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 1\">Advances in Computer Chess 1</a>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_2\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 2\">Advances in Computer Chess 2</a> and Advances in Computer Chess 3 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. He was chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and  <a href=\"/Chess_Problems,_Compositions_and_Studies\" title=\"Chess Problems, Compositions and Studies\">chess composer</a>. Michael Clarke deceased in early 1994 of stomach cancer <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1970_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1970 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1970_...\">1970 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1970 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1970</b>). <i>A rapidly convergent Method for Maximum Likelyhood factor Analysis</i>. Brit. Journal Math. Statis. Psychol. 23</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1973</b>). <i>Some Ideas for a Chess Compiler</i>. Artificial and Human Thinking, reprinted 1988 in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Compendium\" title=\"Computer Chess Compendium\">Computer Chess Compendium</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lewis_Wolpert\">Lewis Wolpert</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://devneuro.org/cdn/people-detail.php?personID=1450\">Amata Hornbruch</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1974</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://academic.oup.com/icb/article/14/2/647/2014123\">Positional Information and Positional Signalling in Hydra</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integrative_and_Comparative_Biology\">Integrative and Comparative Biology</a>, Vol. 14, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i>A quantitative study of KPK</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_1\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 1\">Advances in Computer Chess 1</a>, pp. 108-118</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Max_Bramer\" title=\"Max Bramer\">Max Bramer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1979</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0020737379800139\">A Model for the Representation of Pattern-Knowledge for the Endgame in Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.interaction-design.org/references/periodicals/international_journal_of_man-machine_studies_volume_11.html\">International  Journal of Man-Machine Studies, Vol. 11, No.5</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Don_Beal\" title=\"Don Beal\">Don Beal</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i>The Construction of Economical and Correct Algorithms for King and Pawn against King</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_2\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 2\">Advances in Computer Chess 2</a>, pp. 1-30</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i>The Theory of Coordinate Squares</i>.  <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_2\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 2\">Advances in Computer Chess 2</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://biomet.oxfordjournals.org/content/67/2/441.abstract\">The reduced major axis of a bivariate sample</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biometrika\">Biometrika</a>, Vol. 67, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jstor.org/pss/2346398\">A Givens Algorithm for Moving from one Linear Model to another without Going back to the Data</a></i>. Algorithm AS 163 <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1982</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jstor.org/pss/2347983\">The Gauss-Jordan Sweep Operator with Detection of Collinearity</a></i>. Algorithm AS 178 <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dl.acm.org/author_page.cfm?id=81100261904&amp;coll=DL&amp;dl=GUIDE&amp;CFID=45827860&amp;CFTOKEN=45681320\">Jagdish J. Modi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1984</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/l076048v728712l6/\">An Alternative Givens Ordering</a></i>. Numerische Mathematik, Vol. 43, No. 1 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/~stever/\">Steve Reeves</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1990, 2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/~stever/LCS.html\">Logic for Computer Science</a></i>. </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/w38j2u6u40310t38/\">Conditionals, uncertain rules and belief revision</a></i>. Artificial Intelligence Review, Volume 5, Numbers 1-2</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=158507\">Erricos John Kontoghiorghes</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pubzone.org/dblp/conf/parco/KontoghiorghesC93\">A Parallel Algorithm for Repeated Processing Estimation of Linear Models with Equality Constraints</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/parco/parco1993.html#KontoghiorghesC93\">PARCO 1993</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=158507\">Erricos John Kontoghiorghes</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/f37823284hh143jl/\">Computing the Complete Orthogonal Decomposition Using a SIMD Array Processor</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/parle/parle93.html#KontoghiorghesC93\">PARLE 1993</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=158507\">Erricos John Kontoghiorghes</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/10637199308915444\">Solving the Updated and Downdated Ordinary Linear Model on Massively Parallel SIMD Systems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/paapp/paapp1.html#KontoghiorghesC93\">Parallel Algorithms and Applications, Vol. 1, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=158507\">Erricos John Kontoghiorghes</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2947024\">Solving the General Linear Model on a SIMD Array Processor</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/cai/cai14.html#KontoghiorghesC95\">Computers and Artificial Intelligence, Vol. 14, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=158507\">Erricos John Kontoghiorghes</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mike Clarke</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ideas.repec.org/a/eee/csdana/v19y1995i4p369-377.html\">An alternative approach for the numerical solution of seemingly unrelated regression equations models</a></i>. Computational Statistics &amp; Data Analysis, Vol. 19, No. 4</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/MRB._Clarke\">MRB. Clarke chess games - 365Chess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Clarke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institute_of_Computer_Science\">University of London Institute of Computer Science (ICS)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Jack_Good\" title=\"Jack Good\">Jack Good</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1045416.1045430\">Review of \"Advances in Computer Chess, Volume 1. by M.R.B. Clarke\"; University Press, 1977</a></i>. ACM SIGART Bulletin, Issue 66</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.librarything.com/author/clarkemrb\">M. R. B. Clarke | LibraryThing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/MRB._Clarke\">MRB. Clarke chess games - 365Chess.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gadycosteff.com/eg/eg111-supplement.pdf\">EG111-supplement May 1994</a> (pdf) by <a href=\"/Gady_Costeff\" title=\"Gady Costeff\">Gady Costeff</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/c/Clarke:M=_R=_B=.html\">DBLP: M. R. B. Clarke</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Givens_rotation\">Givens rotation from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gauss%E2%80%93Jordan_elimination\">Gauss–Jordan elimination from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301034005\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 153/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node co